{{Div col end}}

哈佛大學和鄰近的[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]一直存在著友好的競爭關係，這兩所學校經常有很多合作的研討會和項目，同時也建立了一些共同的研究中心，例如[[哈佛-MIT健康科學與技術部|哈佛-MIT健康科學與技術部]]及{{link-en|博爾研究中心|Broad Institute}}。除了科研，有關學術部門也旨在培訓哈佛醫科生的[[生物|生物]][[醫學|醫學]]研究能力。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=HST Mission |url=http://hst.mit.edu/about/mission |accessdate=2013-06-15 |dead-url=yes |quote=We train our students to carry their engineering and scientific expertise from the laboratory bench to the patient's bedside and to bring clinical insights from the patient's bedside to the laboratory bench. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707062552/http://hst.mit.edu/about/mission |archive-date=2013-07-07 }}</ref> 兩校共同開發的網上課程則包括[[EdX|edX]]。

===捐款回贈===
哈佛大學收到的回贈款額為所有大學中最高。其[[資金|資金]]從2010年9月的二百七十六億六千萬美元，上升至2011年的三百二十億美元，<ref>{{en}}{{Cite journal |title=Harvard Endowment Rises $4.4 Billion to $32 Billion |url=http://harvardmagazine.com/2011/09/harvard-endowment-rises-to-32-billion |journal=Harvard Magazine |accessdate=2011-12-13 |year=2011 |volume=November–December |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111208041304/http://harvardmagazine.com/2011/09/harvard-endowment-rises-to-32-billion |archive-date=2011-12-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 但在這之前的幾年裡，捐款數目有所下降：哈佛宣布在2008—2009年期間收到的回贈下降了22%，<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news |title=Harvard Hit by Loss as Crisis Spreads to Colleges |last=Hechinger |first=John |date=2008-12-04 |work=Wall Street Journal |page=A1}}</ref> 不過之前的報告顯示實際數目應為50%；<ref name="vanity">{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Nina Munk on Hard Times at Harvard |url=http://www.vanityfair.com/politics/features/2009/08/harvard200908?printable=true&currentPage=all |accessdate=2010-08-29 |date=August 2009 |last=Munk |first=Nina |work=Vanity Fair |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100829115742/http://www.vanityfair.com/politics/features/2009/08/harvard200908?printable=true&currentPage=all |archive-date=2010-08-29 }}</ref> [[福布斯|福布斯]]報告裡提到，這意味著該校起碼少了一百二十億美元。<ref name="ForbesUndEnd">{{en}}{{Cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/2009/03/03/harvard-university-investment-opinions-contributors_endowment.html |title=Understanding Endowments, Part I |author=Andrew M. Rosenfield |date=2009-03-04 |work=Forbes |accessdate=2010-08-29 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604153054/http://www.forbes.com/2009/03/03/harvard-university-investment-opinions-contributors_endowment.html |archive-date=2009-06-04 }}</ref> 此財政問題也導致哈佛的奧爾斯頓新校區建築工程遲遲未能開始，原本計劃在2011年落成、耗資十二億的科學大樓也未能在原定時間內完工。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news |url=http://www.thecrimson.com/article/2009/3/5/residents-protest-vacancies-in-allston-span/ |title=Residents Protest Vacancies in Allston |author=Vidya B. Viswanathan and Peter F. Zhu |date=2009-03-05 |newspaper=Harvard Crimson |accessdate=2011-02-10 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429025755/http://www.thecrimson.com/article/2009/3/5/residents-protest-vacancies-in-allston-span/ |archive-date=2011-04-29 }}</ref>

2014年9月16日，哈佛宣布[[恒隆集团|恒隆集团]]董事长[[陈启宗|陈启宗]]及其弟[[陈乐宗|陈乐宗]]捐赠三亿五千万美元给[[哈佛公共衛生學院|哈佛公共衛生學院]]，后者改名为“哈佛陈曾熙公共卫生学院”以纪念陈氏兄弟父亲、恒隆集团创始人[[陈曾熙|陈曾熙]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=The story of T.H. Chan |url=https://www.hsph.harvard.edu/magazine/magazine_article/the-story-of-t-h-chan/ |accessdate=2019-03-23 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323175508/https://www.hsph.harvard.edu/magazine/magazine_article/the-story-of-t-h-chan/ |archive-date=2019-03-23 }}</ref>。

2015年6月3日，哈佛宣布避險基金經理[[约翰·保尔森|约翰·保尔森]]（John Paulson）捐贈四億美元給哈佛工程與應用工程學院，打破2014年陈氏兄弟记录，而工程學院也改名為「哈佛約翰鮑爾森工程與應用科學學院」（Harvard John A. Paulson School of Engineering and Applied Sciences）。鮑爾森是1980年哈佛商學院的畢業生，這是哈佛建校379年以來最高額的捐款。
<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.worldjournal.com/3272380/article-shortlink/ |title=哈佛獲捐4億 破港富豪捐款紀錄 |accessdate=2016-08-25 |archive-date=2016-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928124648/http://www.worldjournal.com/3272380/article-shortlink/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
<ref>{{Cite web |title=哈佛大學收4億美金捐款 史上最大筆 |url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%94%B64%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E9%87%91%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%AD%86-002300246.html |accessdate=2018-10-28 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028074102/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%94%B64%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E9%87%91%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE-%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%AD%86-002300246.html |archive-date=2018-10-28 }}</ref>
<ref>{{Cite web |title=哈佛獲校史最大筆捐款 華爾街富豪捐120億 |url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20150604002996-260408 |accessdate=2018-10-28 |last=中時電子報 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028190248/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20150604002996-260408 |archive-date=2018-10-28 }}</ref>
<ref>{{Cite web |title=打破校史捐款記錄，哈佛大學獲4億美金捐款 - The News Lens 關鍵評論網 |url=http://www.thenewslens.com/article/17954 |accessdate=2018-10-28 |date=2015-06-04 |last=吳象元 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028190259/https://www.thenewslens.com/article/17954 |archive-date=2018-10-28 }}</ref>

=== 校訓 ===
哈佛早期的校訓是「'''真理'''」（{{lang|en|Veritas}}，1643年）、「'''榮耀歸於基督'''」（{{lang|en|In Christ Gloriam}}，1650年），以及「'''為基督·為教會'''」（{{lang|en|Christo et Ecclesiae}}，1692年）；印章展示三本翻開的書本，兩本面向上，一本面向下，象徵着理性（{{lang|en|reason}}）與啟示（{{lang|en|revelation}}）之間的互動。一份最早期的文獻——1642年的學院法例寫道：「讓每一位學生都認真考慮以認識神與耶穌基督為永生之源（約17:3），作為他人生與學習的主要目標，因而以基督作為一切正統知識和學習的惟一基礎。所有人既看見主賜下智慧，便當在隱密處認真藉著禱告尋求他的智慧。」<ref>{{Cite book |title=我在哈佛遇見神 |last=莫莱（{{lang|en|Kelly Monroe}}）}}</ref> 這些校訓都是在美國建國前的宗教單一時期定下的。

後來，為符合聖經尊重全人類自由意志但需提供平等的知識受教權發展的學術自由原則，美國取消了基督宗教的唯一性，以宗教中立取而代之。追求真理和發展科學文化教育的事業逐漸興旺，哈佛大學校訓最終確定為「真理」。

==學術泛論==
===招生===
哈佛的招生以“高篩選、低轉入”見稱。大學部哈佛學院2017學年課程的錄取率僅為5.8%，為全美最難入讀的大學之一。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Harvard College Accepts Record Low of 5.8 Percent to the Class of 2017 | News | The Harvard Crimson |url=http://www.thecrimson.com/article/2013/3/28/class-of-2017-admissions/ |accessdate=2013-07-05 |last=Yaqhubi |first=Zohra D. |publisher=Thecrimson.com |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617113023/http://www.thecrimson.com/article/2013/3/28/class-of-2017-admissions/ |archive-date=2013-06-17 }}</ref> 據統計，有95%獲錄取的大學新生為[[高中|高中]]成績及課外活動參與率十強的記錄保持者。哈佛在2009年賦予了266名學生美國國家精英獎學金，人數為全美高校之冠。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Colleges With the Most Freshman Merit Scholars, 2009 |url=http://chronicle.com/article/Chart-Colleges-With-the-Mo/124012/ |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=The Chronicle of Higher Education |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120114153539/http://chronicle.com/article/Chart-Colleges-With-the-Mo/124012/ |archive-date=2012-01-14 }}</ref>

===教學===
哈佛大學為一所面積遼闊及有高住宿率的綜合型研究大學。<ref name="Carnegie">{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Carnegie Classifications - Harvard University |url=http://classifications.carnegiefoundation.org/lookup_listings/view_institution.php?unit_id=166027 |accessdate=2010-08-08 |publisher=The Carnegie Foundation for the Advancement of Teaching |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429025702/http://classifications.carnegiefoundation.org/lookup_listings/view_institution.php?unit_id=166027 |archive-date=2011-04-29 }}</ref>早在1929年就已經獲得美國[[新英格蘭學校聯會|新英格蘭學校聯會]]（{{lang|en|NEASC}}）的認可。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Roster of Institutions |url=http://cihe.neasc.org/about_our_institutions/roster_of_institutions/ |accessdate=2010-08-28 |publisher=Commission on Institutions of Higher Education, New England Association of Schools and Colleges |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828132004/http://cihe.neasc.org/about_our_institutions/roster_of_institutions/ |archivedate=2013-08-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 大學現在提供46個[[學士|學士]]主修課程、<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Fields of Concentration |url=http://www.handbook.fas.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&tabgroupid=icb.tabgroup106995 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=Handbook for Students |publisher=Harvard College |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120803025109/http://www.handbook.fas.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&tabgroupid=icb.tabgroup106995 |archivedate=2012-08-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 134個[[研究生|研究生]]課程<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Degree Programs |url=http://www.gsas.harvard.edu/images/stories/pdfs/handbook.pdf |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=Graduate School of Arts and Sciences Handbook |pages=28–30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909232153/http://www.gsas.harvard.edu/images/stories/pdfs/handbook.pdf |archivedate=2015-09-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 及32個專業課程（[[醫學|醫]]、[[法律學|法]]等）。<ref name="Degrees" /> 在2008-2009年期間，哈佛共頒發了1664個[[學士|學士]]學位、400個[[碩士|碩士]]學位、512個[[博士|博士]]學位及4460個專業學位。<ref name="Degrees">{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Degrees Conferred by Program: Academic Year 2008–2009 |url=http://www.provost.harvard.edu/institutional_research/Provost_-_FB2009_10_Sec02_Completions.pdf |accessdate=2010-08-28 |publisher=Institutional Research, Office of the Provost, Harvard University |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100611223134/http://www.provost.harvard.edu/institutional_research/Provost_-_FB2009_10_Sec02_Completions.pdf |archivedate=2010-06-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 

學士的入學申請人數其實只佔了整體的很少一部分，學士課程主要為藝術及理學範疇（美國不少專業課程只供學士畢業生修讀）。在1978-2008年期間，所有學士生需完成七門主修以外的課程，<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Academic Information: The Core Curricilum Requirement |url=http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343094 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=Handbook for Students |publisher=Harvard College |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205233348/http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343094 |archivedate=2010-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 作為核心課程的一部分；之後課程有變動，在2008年之後，所有學士生除了主修課程，還需完成八類的大學[[通識教育|通識教育]]課程，它們分別是：美學與理解、文化與信仰、數學與簡化解釋、道德理解、生命科學、物理科學、世界與社會及美國與世界。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Academic Information: Program in General Education Requirement |url=http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343093 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=Handbook for Students |publisher=Harvard College |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205233356/http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343093 |archivedate=2010-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 另一方面，哈佛的研究生課程則非常多元化，並與其學士生課程有很大的關聯。不過，有某一部分的學生及教育組織批評哈佛的學士生課程過於依賴[[助教|助教]]，指這樣會影響教育質素。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news |url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9803E5D71130F933A1575AC0A9649C8B63 |title=Should Our Colleges Be Ranked? |last=Hicks |first=D. L. |date=2002-09-20 |work=The New York Times |dead-url=no |access-date=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070211024557/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9803E5D71130F933A1575AC0A9649C8B63 |archive-date=2007-02-11 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Grade Inflation: It's Not Just an Issue for the Ivy League |url=http://www.carnegiefoundation.org/perspectives/perspectives2004.June.htm |last=Merrow |first=J. |year=2004 |work=Carnegie Perspectives |publisher=The Carnegie Foundation for the Advancement of Teaching |dead-url=no |access-date=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623123609/http://www.carnegiefoundation.org/perspectives/perspectives2004.June.htm |archive-date=2013-06-23 }}</ref>

哈佛採用[[學期|學期制]]教學，每個學年從九月初開始直到五月中旬，分上下兩個學期。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Handbook for students--Academic Calendar |url=http://handbook.fas.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k88702&tabgroupid=icb.tabgroup147399 |accessdate=2013-06-15 |publisher=Harvard University}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 學士生在每個學期/半學年裡需完成四門指定科目，並須保持這個報讀率以維持作為全職學士生的資格。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Academic Information: Rate of Work |url=http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343175 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=Handbook for Students |publisher=Harvard College |archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20101205234223/http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343175 |archivedate=2010-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 每個主修科目均提供基礎課程及高級課程供學生選擇。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Academic Information: The Concentration Requirement |url=http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343095 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=Handbook for Students |publisher=Harvard College |archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20101205233358/http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343095 |archivedate=2010-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 以排名首4-5%成績畢業的學生會獲賦予最高榮譽「{{lang|en|summa cum laude}}」學位證明，剩下的前15%的學生獲「{{lang|en|magna cum laude}}」的頭銜，其餘的30%則為「{{lang|en|cum laude}}」。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Academic Information: Requirements for Honors Degrees |url=http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343182 |accessdate=2010-08-28 |work=Handbook for Students |publisher=Harvard College |archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20101205234250/http://isites.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do?keyword=k69286&pageid=icb.page343182 |archivedate=2010-12-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 大學不同學科部均有不同的獎學金及獎項頒發。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=FINANCIAL AID OFFICE |url=http://www.fao.fas.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do |accessdate=2013-06-14 |publisher=Harvard University |dead-url=yes |quote=...has provided assistance to students who need help in meeting their education expenses for over 350 years, enabling us to seek out the most outstanding scholars in the world |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130328184603/http://www.fao.fas.harvard.edu/icb/icb.do |archive-date=2013-03-28 }}</ref> 惟近年哈佛及很多其他的美國大學被批評出現「等級通脹」的情況，很多獎學金及榮譽的要求不斷上升，<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/magazine/articles/2008/10/05/doesnt_anybody_get_a_c_anymore/ |title=Doesn't Anybody Get a C Anymore? |last=Primack |first=Phil |date=2008-10-05 |newspaper=The Boston Globe |dead-url=no |access-date=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102163409/http://www.boston.com/bostonglobe/magazine/articles/2008/10/05/doesnt_anybody_get_a_c_anymore/ |archive-date=2013-11-02 }}</ref> 例如：哈佛學院獲得[[拉丁文學位榮譽|拉丁文學位榮譽]]的學生人數從2004年的90%，下降至2005年的60%。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Brevia |url=http://harvardmagazine.com/2003/01/brevia.html |accessdate=2013-12-15 |date=January–February 2003 |year=2003 |publisher=Harvard Magazine |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216055215/http://harvardmagazine.com/2003/01/brevia.html |archive-date=2013-12-16 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Grade Inflation is Real |url=http://www.thecrimson.com/fmarchives/fm_03_01_2001/article4A.html |accessdate=2013-12-15 |author=Milzoff, R. M., Paley, A. R., & Reed, B. J. |date=2001-03-01 |year=2001 |publisher=Fifteen Minutes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050204131059/http://www.thecrimson.com/fmarchives/fm_03_01_2001/article4A.html |archivedate=2005-02-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite book |title=At Harvard, more concern for top grades. |last=Bombardieri, M. & Schweitzer, S. |publisher=The Boston Globe |year=February 12, 2006 |quote=Benedict Gross quotes, 23.7% A/25% A- figures, characterized as an "all-time high."}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Princeton becomes first to formally combat grade inflation |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/education/2004-04-26-princeton-grades_x.htm |accessdate=2013-12-15 |author=USA Today |date=2004-04-26 |publisher=Associated Press. |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114023055/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/education/2004-04-26-princeton-grades_x.htm |archive-date=2012-11-14 }}</ref> 不過，也有報告指出，學生們的學習動力及拼搏精神卻因此得以提升。<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news |url=http://www.alfiekohn.org/teaching/gi.htm |title=The Dangerous Myth of Grade Inflation |last=Kohn |first=A |date=2002-11-08 |newspaper=The Chronicle of Higher Education |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060409113947/http://www.alfiekohn.org/teaching/gi.htm |archivedate=2006-04-09 |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2013-05-17 }}</ref>

2009-2010年的哈佛學士學費為33696美元，若加上住宿等生活雜費的話則為48868美元。<ref name="Tuition">{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Tuition at Harvard Schools: FY1990 – FY2010 |url=http://www.provost.harvard.edu/institutional_research/Provost_-_FB2009_10_Sec03_Tuition.pdf |accessdate=2010-08-28 |publisher=Harvard University |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101010174710/http://www.provost.harvard.edu/institutional_research/Provost_-_FB2009_10_Sec03_Tuition.pdf |archivedate=2010-10-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 2007年起哈佛實行財政援助計劃：所有家庭年收入低於六萬美元的學生一律免學費及住宿費，收入介乎六萬-八萬美元的則每年只需繳付數千元的學費。哈佛還宣布，收入在十二萬-十八萬美元的，學費為其家庭每年收入的10%。<ref name="free">{{en}}{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/10/education/10cnd-harvard.html |title=Harvard Steps Up Financial Aid |first=Sara |date=2007-12-10 |last2=Finder |first2=Alan |newspaper=The New York Times |dead-url=no |last1=Rimer |access-date=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109011933/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/10/education/10cnd-harvard.html |archive-date=2015-01-09 }}</ref> 2009年，哈佛授予了總計4.141億美元的獎學金。<ref name="Tuition" />

===圖書館及博物館===
[[File:Widener_Library.jpg|left]]
哈佛大學圖書館的中央系統位於哈佛庭院的[[懷德納圖書館|懷德納圖書館]]內，整個系統覆蓋80所不同的圖書館，整體館藏量超過1600萬冊，使其成為全美最大的[[學術|學術]]圖書館網絡，同時位居全美第三（僅次於[[美國國會圖書館|美國國會圖書館]]和波士顿公共圖書館）<ref name=library/>。不同的圖書館適合不同類型的讀者進入：位處於劍橋市本部的加博科學圖書館（{{lang|en|Cabot Science Library}}）、拉蒙特圖書館（{{lang|en|Lamont Library}}）及懷德納圖書館為大學生最常去的圖書館；霍頓圖書館（{{lang|en|Houghton Library}}）及亚瑟·伊麗莎白施莱辛格圖書館（{{lang|en|Arthur and Elizabeth Schlesinger Library}}）專門收藏有關美國女性地位發展的歷史參考；哈佛大學資料庫搜羅了各種珍貴的書籍及手抄搞；美國一些最古老的地圖、地名冊等能在哈佛的蒲賽圖書館（{{lang|en|Pusey Library}}）內找到；而[[哈佛燕京圖書館|哈佛燕京圖書館]]內則保管與[[東亞|東亞]]古老語言相涉的文獻。
<div style="max-width:1000px;">
