各類綜合排行榜中，《世界大學學術排名》與《泰晤士世界聲譽排名》自首次發佈以來，均一直將哈佛列為最佳學府。<ref name="ARWU">{{Cite web |title=Academic Ranking of World Universities——Harvard University Ranking Profile |url=http://www.shanghairanking.com/World-University-Rankings/Harvard-University.html |accessdate=2016-09-07 |publisher=Shanghai Ranking Consultancy |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160908191702/http://www.shanghairanking.com/World-University-Rankings/Harvard-University.html |archive-date=2016-09-08 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=World Reputation Rankings 2016 |url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2016/reputation-ranking#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank_label/sort_order/asc/cols/rank_only |accessdate=2016-09-07 |year=2016 |publisher=[[泰晤士高等教育|Times Higher Education]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509045436/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2016/reputation-ranking#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank_label/sort_order/asc/cols/rank_only |archive-date=2019-05-09 }}</ref>2003至2009年期間，QS 與《泰晤士高等教育》曾合作發表《[[泰晤士高等教育-QS世界大學排名|泰晤士高等教育-QS世界大學排名]]》，哈佛同樣每年位處榜首。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Brown slips in world university rankings |url=http://www.pbn.com/detail/45410.html |accessdate=2016-09-07 |author=Ted Nesi |date=2009-10-09 |work=Providence Business News |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091015103940/http://www.pbn.com/detail/45410.html |archivedate=2009-10-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

至於個別指標調查，《2015-16年大學學術成就排名》及2011年《國立巴黎高等礦業學校：世界大學專業排名》評哈佛大學為第一（後者計算持[[財富世界500強|財富世界500強]]公司總裁一職的校友人數）。<ref>{{Cite web |title=2015-2016 WORLD RANKING (1-250) |url=http://www.urapcenter.org/2015/world.php?q=MS0yNTA= |accessdate=2016-09-07 |year=2015 |publisher=University Ranking by Academic Performance (URAP) Research Laboratory |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160912043152/http://www.urapcenter.org/2015/world.php?q=MS0yNTA= |archive-date=2016-09-12 }}</ref>根據2016年《[[普林斯頓評論|普林斯頓評論]]》的調查，此校為全美學生與家長心中的「第二夢想學府」。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.princetonreview.com/press/college-hopes-worries-press-release |title=College Hopes & Worries Press Release |accessdate=2016-09-07 |year=2016 |agency=PR Newswire |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919064436/http://www.princetonreview.com/press/college-hopes-worries-press-release |archive-date=2016-09-19 }}</ref>哈佛於由 {{lang|en|PayScale}} 舉辦的2016年《最具價值學府報告》中，位列全國第二十二位。<ref>{{Cite web |title=College ROI Report: Best Value Colleges |url=http://www.payscale.com/college-roi |accessdate=2016-09-07 |year=2016 |agency=PayScale |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909025810/http://www.payscale.com/college-roi |archive-date=2016-09-09 }}</ref>

==校園生活==
===學生群體===
{|style="text-align:center; float:left; font-size:85%; margin-right:1.5em;" class="wikitable"
|+學生人口統計<ref name="Head count">{{en}}{{Cite web |title=Degree Student Head Count: Fall 2010 |url=http://www.provost.harvard.edu/institutional_research/harvard_fact_book_2010-11_web.pdf |accessdate=2013-03-11 |publisher=Harvard University |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130418035745/http://www.provost.harvard.edu/institutional_research/harvard_fact_book_2010-11_web.pdf |archivedate=2013-04-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
